Meter Reader
Installation of ImagePi, Tesseract for Automated Meter Reader

Laurent Balmelli - 7/1/2017
------------------

1. Connect PiCamera
2. Activate PiCamera in Preferences and reboot
3. Install python library for image process
    >sudo apt-get install python-dev
    



>sudo apt-get install tesseract-ocr

To install PIP (Image library)


>tar xvf Imaging-1.1.7.tar.gz
>sudo python setup.py install

git clone https://github.com/madmaze/pytesseract.git

sudo apt-get install libjpeg-dev zlib1g-dev
pip install pillow --upgrade
pip install pytesseract

